How to build this documentation
===============================

1. Have Python
2. Have and activate a python virtualenv (optional)
3. Have the Sphinx python package (pip install sphinx)
4. in this directory:

  make html

5. View generated html documentation in the build/html/ directory
6. Optinally, serve the html with python's built-in http server by entering the build/html directory and doing:

  python -m SimpleHTTPServer 8000
